OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FMainly dry
OL,6,Fthis evening with some late sunshine.
OL,7,FThe rest of the night will be largely
OL,8,Fdry with clear spells, a few light
OL,9,Fshowers in the north and west.
OL,10,
OL,11,CMonday:FMainly dry with variable
OL,12,Famounts of cloud and a few bright
OL,13,Fspells. The odd light shower in
OL,14,Fnorthwest. Outbreaks of rain spreading
OL,15,Fnortheast in the evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
