OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:
OL,6,FScattered slow moving showers on
OL,7,FTuesday, occasionally heavy. Mainly
OL,8,Fdry on Wednesday, a little light rain
OL,9,Flikely later. A few showers at first
OL,10,Fon Thursday, otherwise dry.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
